New Delhi, the 5th November, 1951.

The undersigned is directed to inform Cabinet
Ministers that Dr. K.N. Katju has assumed the office of
Cabinet Minister with effect from the 5th November, 1951,
and will hold charge of the Ministry of Home Affairs and
the Ministry of Law.
